00:07:57.111 --> 00:08:02.950 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:02.984 --> 00:08:08.389 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:08.422 --> 00:08:10.558 position:24% line:89% align:start
