00:09:06.515 --> 00:09:08.783 position:13% line:83% align:start
As long as I could have you
near me.

00:09:08.816 --> 00:09:12.119 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Crying]
That's all...I ever wanted.

00:09:12.153 --> 00:09:16.857 position:10% line:83% align:start
