to being all alone in the world.

00:09:18.793 --> 00:09:22.563 position:41% line:83% align:start
Please.
I don't want to be alone.

00:09:22.596 --> 00:09:24.231 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not again.

00:09:24.265 --> 00:09:27.201 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't leave me!

00:09:27.234 --> 00:09:29.637 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm begging you!

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:33.607 position:5% line:83% align:start
Helena: That man told me
it had to be this way.

00:09:33.641 --> 00:09:36.444 position:47% line:83% align:start
Who said that?
What man?

00:09:36.477 --> 00:09:39.647 position:55% line:83% align:start
You mean
that butler Franz?

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:42.650 position:13% line:83% align:start
"The father...
is destined to be him."

00:09:42.683 --> 00:09:46.954 position:10% line:83% align:start
