must be born of a king.

00:09:46.987 --> 00:09:53.227 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:53.260 --> 00:09:59.100 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:59.133 --> 00:10:03.505 position:7% line:83% align:start
Please, don't cry,
my dear Abel Bluefield.

00:10:03.538 --> 00:10:06.941 position:5% line:83% align:start
