It's over.

00:10:06.974 --> 00:10:11.312 position:5% line:83% align:start
And so I must return
to Eden.

00:10:11.345 --> 00:10:12.847 position:61% line:89% align:start
Eden?

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:17.318 position:13% line:83% align:start
If I journey there, will I be
able to see you again?

00:10:17.351 --> 00:10:23.491 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:23.525 --> 00:10:25.426 position:5% line:89% align:start
Any who have a calling...

00:10:25.459 --> 00:10:27.928 position:5% line:89% align:start
will be guided to Eden.

00:10:27.962 --> 00:10:30.565 position:16% line:83% align:start
I cannot say
with certainty, though,

00:10:30.599 --> 00:10:33.535 position:13% line:83% align:start
