[ Gasps ]

00:10:35.436 --> 00:10:37.004 position:10% line:83% align:start
...if there ever
comes a time

00:10:37.037 --> 00:10:39.406 position:5% line:83% align:start
where your path crosses
with the child...

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:43.477 position:5% line:83% align:start
