that you also have a calling.

00:10:43.512 --> 00:10:48.716 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:50.651 --> 00:10:53.687 position:5% line:89% align:start
Goodbye for now, Abel.

00:10:53.721 --> 00:10:57.258 position:5% line:83% align:start
